HEADWORD: Magnificat
<hw>Mag*nif"i*cat</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., it
magnifies.]</ety> <def>The song of the Virgin Mary, <au>Luke i. 46</au>;
-- so called because it commences with this word in the
Vulgate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Magnificate</ent>⟦br⟧
